name: David Hollis
description:
I believe happiness is a state of mind. I am a friendly, outgoing person who love life.I am here to make new friend and to learn more about this big, beautiful world of ours.
I am looking forward meeting a woman of my dream, someone who is ready to walk with me through this journey of life. A woman with passion, love and understanding, life is short lets make it sweet!!.
My height is 175cm, i like to keep my hair low most time, well i maintain my average body size. My smile will make you fall for me always i believe this is my best feature, i also like to dress casual when i am not on official duties.
